title: Washington Today (11-3-22): Kellyanne Conway & Ron Klain on POTUS' 'democracy is on the ballot'

media:group.media:title: Washington Today (11-3-22): Kellyanne Conway & Ron Klain on POTUS' 'democracy is on the ballot'
media:group.media:description:
Former WH Counselor Kellyanne Conway & WH COS Ron Klain on President Biden's warning "democracy is on the ballot", interview with USA Today's Ken Tran on health care as election issue (14), U.S. & South Korea extend military exercises after North Korean missile launches.
